<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>وَكَافِئْنَ ذَوِي الْمَعْرُوفِ مَا صَنَعُوا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>إِنَّ الصَّنَائِعَ بِالأَحْرَارِ كَالْمَطَر<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَلا تَكُنْ سَبخًا لَمْ يِجِدْ مَاطِرَهُ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَكُنْ كَرَوْضٍ أَتَى بِالزَّهْرِ وَالثَّمَرِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَاذْكُرْ صَنِيعةَ حُرٍّ حَازَ عَنْكَ غِنَى<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَقَدْ تَقَاضَيْتَهُ فِي زِيّ مُفْتَقَرِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَاحْفَظْ ذِمَام صَدِيقٍ كُنْتَ تَأْلَفُهُ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَذِمَّةَ الْجَارِ صُنْهَا عَنْ يَدِ الْغَيْرِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَصْلْ أَخا رَحِمٍ تَكْسَبْ مَوَدَّتُهُ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَفَي الْخُطُوبِ تَرَاهُ خَيْر مُنْتَصِر<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَوَصْلُهُ قَدْ يَجُرُّ الْوَصْلَ فِي عَقِبٍ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَقَدْ يَزْادُ بِهِ فِي مُدَّةِ الْعُمُرِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَجُدْ عَلَى سَائِلٍ وَافَى بِذِلَّتِهِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَلَوْ بِشَيْءٍ قَلِيلِ النَّفْع مُحْتَقَر<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَاحْفَظْ أَمَانَة مَنْ أَبْدَى سَرِيرَتُهُ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>مَالاً وَحَالاً لِحُسْنِ الظَّنِ وَالنَّظَرِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَاقرِ الضُّيُوفَ وَكُنْ عَبْدًا لِخِدْمَتِهِمْ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَهُشُّ بِشَّ وَلا تَسْأَلْ عَنِ السَّفَرِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَبَادِرْنَ إِلَيْهِمْ بِالَّذِي اقْتَرَحُوا<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>عَنْ طِيبِ نَفْسٍ بِلا مَنٍّ وَلا كَدَرِ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>وَخُضْ بِهِمْ فِي فُنُونٍ يَأْنَسُونَ بِهَا<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>مِنْ كُلِّ مَا طَابَ لِلأَسْمَاعِ فِي السَّمَر<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>